TEXT.S:
Gongxidaye(u kamu nu Lipun: Gongxidaye, 1956 a mihcaan-) i Lipun jing gang xian qing shui ding lecuhen u misakulitay a kulit tu cudad a tatama.
kalilimani Lipun mamin micudad tu talawkaway a cacudadan, Gongxidaye mamusakawaw tu sikulitay a misangaay tu kulitu nu tademaw a kulit a kawaw nida. sisa Gongxidaye malinga tu tu pasayni nu wawaan a kuit misanga, mamin sa 1999 a mihcaan wucu nu buyu i kilakilangan makaadih tu adidiay a kiwma nu kungku <kapah ayda sakapahay a nikalalitemuh>kyu makaala tu tuluway a sakasengan a kawlah nu kulit.
2003 a mihcaan Gongxidaye yadah kuni papeluwan tu konglong a sasakamuwan <u nu konglong a kulit tayamin>, tu nu sayaway <adihen mayda asu'ay>sisa 2010 a mihcaan misumat tu misaungaay a kacudu; u luma a mihcaan tu cacay a bataan a bulad i nakulikulitan i Toykui a tilibi <Gongxidaye pakaluwaluwah adihen mayda asu'ay>Gongxidaye pakaluwaluwah a adihan misanga tu misaungaay a tilibi paadih. 2015 a mihcaan tu waluay a bulad<u sakasaetimen naku a wawa kisu>makaycu tu mala kacudu misaungaay inga.matatulin kina kawaw nida mikulit tu cudad, Gongxidaye misanga tu nu wawa a sapasubana tu sikulitay a cudadsawni nisulit; atu nu Lipun a sipakungku i tatacuwacuwa.
nilacul
